{"tid":301832,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"李小加：香港無本土化市場必須依靠內地","createTime":"2017-06-29T02:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T13:35:50.000Z","uid":24660,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c77cd00b227fcbbf4c624d8a9fad9c1793ee87","tid":301832,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:42:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港交所行政總裁李小加接受訪問時表示，本港發展必須依靠內地。他以沙特阿美上市為例，如果內地認為時機不適合，沙特阿美來港上市的機會便會降低。<br />\n<br />\n一直強調香港是內地與世界連接的轉換器，李小加過去數年藉着這個定位促成了互聯互通，他認為未來香港要繼續游走於中國與世界之間，因為香港並沒有本土化市場。<br />\n<br />\n他以市傳集資高達1000億美元的阿拉伯石油公司沙特阿美計劃上市為例，港交所爭取它來市上市，亦要說服對方香港能如何滿足各方利益，包括中國的利益。因為目前只有香港可以透過互聯互通的方式，串連起內地及沙特阿美。<br />\n<br />\n李小加表示，新股通需要一件標誌性的事件來推動，而沙特阿美上市就是其中之一。他又期望明年可能先在香港推動A股的海外衍生工具市場，但對於有批評指，更多內地資金來港令市場質素進一步轉差，李小加不認為港交所要交出監管權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=226545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226545&d=O6IRHH6heEBx9e2wK3qu4TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1c7afb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D226545&h=38dbe6af\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=226545</a>"},{"pid":"7d21db2a22c09aa578d5c23d4ed333158bb11c0e","tid":301832,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"近5年垃圾中國股一大堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be7e7ed87e1fa7852adc92f2956b8d51a97764","tid":301832,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"其實係有國際股加國企都夠香港愛多八十年"},{"pid":"a0e9eb5605932e377c0092c1895e8aca69ba5aa3","tid":301832,"uid":125688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"最緊要有成交,有公司上市,理得靠邊個,有奶便是娘"},{"pid":"ef907475d8cfd4b46063aab6f4972013d60d6826","tid":301832,"uid":112226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:40:22.000Z","msg":"股票市場無話本唔本土市場<br />\n<br />\n有錢賺既公司黎上市咪得"},{"pid":"cd7719cd8814309f6dfc01a4e7e6ce241d114a59","tid":301832,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"香港人食緊魚翅時，中國人還食緊樹皮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4efb69149bf31790592da0d8cbd953e238de08","tid":301832,"uid":9069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"拎沙特黎比⋯"},{"pid":"309f4a820dfd9ed637b3e80958c5c9df35e8f34b","tid":301832,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T13:35:50.000Z","msg":"水至濁則無魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}